com.camerontec.catalys.core.marketstate

Class ReferenceNotFoundException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.camerontec.catalys.core.marketstate.ReferenceNotFoundException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ReferenceNotFoundException
extends Exception
    Exception thrown when the market mirror can't find an object that is referenced by a message. E.g., If an execution report is received that references an order that does not exist in the market mirror.
    Author:
    Hugh Emberson
